After over a year of hard work and extraordinary effort by our team here, we are very excited to release our new rear diffusers! We have made significant improvements over our old design from the ground up, including Carbon Fiber PETG mounting brackets, stainless steel hardware & finishing washers, full ACM construction for durability & strength, laser engraved main panels, & custom instructions tailor made for your specific vehicle. These diffusers give a sleek, aggressive design, and are available for many popular applications like the S197/S550 Mustang, MKV Supra, Evo X, Civic Type R, Q50, Toyota 86, and more, with new designs being added every week.
